propAlign: Set the text-align on the component.
propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propColor: The color of the component. It supports those theme colors that make sense for this component.
propComponent:
The component used for the root node.
Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propGutterBottom: If `true`, the text will have a bottom margin.
propNoWrap:
If `true`, the text will not wrap, but instead will truncate with a text overflow ellipsis.

Note that text overflow can only happen with block or inline-block level elements
(the element needs to have a width in order to overflow).
propParagraph: If `true`, the text will have a bottom margin.
propVariantMapping:
The component maps the variant prop to a range of different HTML element types.
For instance, subtitle1 to `<h6>`.
If you wish to change that mapping, you can provide your own.
Alternatively, you can use the `component` prop.
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesBody2: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="body2"`.
stylesBody1: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="body1"`.
stylesCaption: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="caption"`.
stylesButton: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="button"`.
stylesH1: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="h1"`.
stylesH2: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="h2"`.
stylesH3: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="h3"`.
stylesH4: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="h4"`.
stylesH5: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="h5"`.
stylesH6: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="h6"`.
stylesSubtitle1: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="subtitle1"`.
stylesSubtitle2: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="subtitle2"`.
stylesOverline: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="overline"`.
stylesInherit: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="inherit"`.
stylesAlignLeft: Styles applied to the root element if `align="left"`.
stylesAlignCenter: Styles applied to the root element if `align="center"`.
stylesAlignRight: Styles applied to the root element if `align="right"`.
stylesAlignJustify: Styles applied to the root element if `align="justify"`.
stylesNoWrap: Styles applied to the root element if `nowrap={true}`.
stylesGutterBottom: Styles applied to the root element if `gutterBottom={true}`.
stylesParagraph: Styles applied to the root element if `paragraph={true}`.
stylesColorInherit: Styles applied to the root element if `color="inherit"`.
stylesColorPrimary: Styles applied to the root element if `color="primary"`.
stylesColorSecondary: Styles applied to the root element if `color="secondary"`.
stylesColorTextPrimary: Styles applied to the root element if `color="textPrimary"`.
stylesColorTextSecondary: Styles applied to the root element if `color="textSecondary"`.
stylesColorError: Styles applied to the root element if `color="error"`.
stylesDisplayInline: Styles applied to the root element if `display="inline"`.
stylesDisplayBlock: Styles applied to the root element if `display="block"`.
